metadata.name: Guipure 1/1
metadata.description:
Pre-programmed choices of a murkier sort overridden by contagious independence. Grace, poise and the elegant mystique of the gypsy contemporary. Will over fate. Lavishly attuned to a delicately layered exotic style. Shimmering silver gemstones scattered amongst teal green bell feathered earrings. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful young 24 year old female model wearing a short red lace dress, pink lipstick, cute green purses, crystal earrings and an orange bandana, walking down Manhattan in the 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
